{"tid":1873151,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約同潮流教父開餐　光希鬈毛look似足媽咪","createTime":"2020-02-10T13:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T13:03:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2aaf2734831337cde65b8c9f4be7edf160efd70b","tid":1873151,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200210/photo/bkn-20200210185925136-0210_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200210191431\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200210185925136-0210_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200210191431&h=daac7f43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日劇天王木村拓哉的寶貝女光希，上星期度過17歲牛一後，日前飛到美國開工。她今日在IG上載開工花絮片段，換上鬈髮與濃妝示人，被指似足當年媽咪工藤靜香爆炸頭造型。<br />\n<br />\n此外，工藤靜香亦有陪愛女赴美，她與光希日前便不約而同在IG，上載在紐約與潮流教父藤原浩食飯的合照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200210/photo/bkn-20200210185925136-0210_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200210191431\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200210185925136-0210_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200210191431&h=82b2d66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200210/photo/bkn-20200210185925136-0210_00862_001_03p.jpg?20200210191431\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200210185925136-0210_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20200210191431&h=0397b34c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}